From cou.: 11 For the preparation of the lyotropic nanoparticle solutions, the polymer coated nanoparticles were dissolved in the calculated amount of toluene to obtain a concentration series of 10–90% w/w. From each concentration, 15 μL were transformed into a capillary tube (diameter of 1 mm), which were melted off to avoid solvent evaporation.
From Soup: 11 For the preparation of the lyotropic nanoparticle solutions, the polymer coated nanoparticles were dissolved in the calculated amount of toluene to obtain a concentration series of 10–90% w/w. From each concentration, 15 μL were transformed into a capillary tube (diameter of 1 mm), which were melted off to avoid solvent evaporation .
